metadata.description: Woman is an endless source of inspiration in my craft. Her beauty, power, and courage are what Iâ€™m trying to capture in my work. It is essential for me to show the personality and the spirit of my characters without the surrounding details to let the viewer concentrate on the raw emotion rather than on the explanation. The colour plays a paramount role in my vision, because it helps to get empathy across. It lies at the core of my perception of female nature.
